Interface StatementGroup

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Iterable<Statement>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    StatementGroupFromJson, StatementGroupImpl

    public interface StatementGroup
extends Iterable<Statement>
    A statement group represents an ordered list of Statement objects that use the same subject and the same property in the main snak of their Claim.
    Author:
    Markus Kroetzsch
